thread.title_full: Antique Lamp Supply reviewed by Larry Martin

author: Larry Martin
title: Larry Martin
text: Although one of my orders didn't come with a wiring diagram as promised, they did arrive sooner than expected and with no back orders. I was able to figure out how to wire the switches with the help of an electrician friend and I am satisfied with the quality of the parts I received. I will continue to buy from ALS in the future.
